sn_aia_agent_tool_m2m.description:
This tool returns a dictionary of values extracted for each key in a DocIntel task, for example {"simple_keys": {"first_name": "John", "last_name": "Doe"}}. All entries are under a main one named "simple_keys", and only "simple" keys (not part of a key group) are returned.
Note that it returns whatever is available at the time of the call, whether the task has been reviewed or not. If it is called too early, even the automated extraction might not have had time to run.
If the task record is not marked as "processed", this tool will fail.
